########
HOW TO USE
########

1. change set of crawling sites in ./conf/sites.dat where e.g.:
http://tv.sme.sk /v/ sme.sk

http://tv.sme.sk 		- URL where we will find <a> tags and search in these pages for video content to the depth 1
/v/ 					- regexp for parsing urls with video content
sme.sk 					- name of crawling method (sites have different methods for accessing content)

2. 